1932;;Almost Married;;American;;William Cameron Menzies;;Violet Heming, Ralph Bellamy;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Almost_Married_(1932_film);;A Russian woman with a forged passport attempts to elude the police and seeks the assistance of a man she met one summer in Scotland. She married an official at the British Embassy in Moscow, and settles down with him in England. However she reveals that she is already married, and her husband is criminally insane.